description: Maybe Drivers Are Getting The Message?
maintext: A New Years Eve RIDE program, positioned on Innisfil Beach Road stopped 95 drivers. South Simcoe Police say none of the drivers had been drinking. The same can’t be said for spot Checks between Bradford and Innisfil. 463 cars were stopped at various locations. 21 roadside screening tests were done. Resulting in 3 warns – which means automatic license suspensions.
title: 107.5 Kool FM
